17
00:01:08,131 --> 00:01:09,821
She had a heart attack last night.

18
00:01:12,291 --> 00:01:13,538
A heart attack?

19
00:01:13,571 --> 00:01:14,371
Yes,

20
00:01:14,761 --> 00:01:16,351
that's what the police said.

21
00:01:16,391 --> 00:01:18,871
They even said that she's been dead
since last night.

22
00:01:19,731 --> 00:01:20,961
Who would've known?

23
00:01:21,271 --> 00:01:24,321
She usually sleeps out here,

24
00:01:24,941 --> 00:01:26,951
