28
00:01:40,631 --> 00:01:42,071
My name is not Korn,

29
00:01:44,021 --> 00:01:46,191
and I don't know Jomkwan.

30
00:01:46,811 --> 00:01:49,921
You might not in this life,

31
00:01:50,961 --> 00:01:54,501
but you did in your previous ones.

32
00:01:59,541 --> 00:02:00,901
What do you mean?

33
00:02:01,651 --> 00:02:03,191
I don't get it.

34
00:02:07,141 --> 00:02:08,931
It is you... Mrs. Penn Masri?

35
00:02:12,691 --> 00:02:14,071
I am, ma'am.

36
00:02:16,171 --> 00:02:17,341
The time has come.

37
00:02:18,171 --> 00:02:19,101
We shall take our leave.

38
00:02:19,791 --> 00:02:20,651
Yes.

39
00:02:27,291 --> 00:02:28,521
